      <title>欧洲大型股票正进一步陷入美国大型股的阴影中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/europe-s-big-stocks-are-shrinking-deeper-into-us-megacaps-shadow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺和诺德公司股价暴跌 930 亿美元，给欧洲最大的上市公司带来了最新打击，这些公司又花了一年时间徒劳地努力追赶华尔街最大股票的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/europe-s-big-stocks-are-shrinking-deeper-into-us-megacaps-shadow</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
